## Upselling Workflow

- [ ] 1. Assess current engagement and client needs
- [ ] 2. Identify unmet needs and opportunities
- [ ] 3. Qualify opportunities by fit and timing
- [ ] 4. Develop upsell proposal with value
- [ ] 5. Present in context of existing relationship
- [ ] 6. Follow up and close

